&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Expectations for the course:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;"&gt;You are expected to read and post at least once in each forum (not each discussion thread) and journal; watch recorded presentations; read the &lt;span class="nolink"&gt;background readings &lt;/span&gt;and resource pages of the course; and complete assignments and the final evaluation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
